trans-unit.source: Represents a <see cref="T:System.String" /> property (and its value) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 表示列印系統硬體或軟體元件的 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 屬性 (及其值)。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this class to install a second printer that differs in its properties from an existing printer only in location, port, and shared status.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範如何使用這個類別來安裝不同的第二個印表機屬性與現有印表機只位置、 連接埠，以及共用的狀態。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.String" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> 表示之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 屬性的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 為指定的屬性初始化 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.String> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.String>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Submitter%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Submitter", not "submitter".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Submitter%2A>屬性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>物件必須拼字 「 傳送者 「 不 」 傳送者 」。

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.String" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" /> 表示之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 屬性的名稱。

trans-unit.source: The value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> class that has the specified value for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 初始化指定屬性擁有指定值之 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 類別的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.String> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName`拼字應該做為某些特定的名稱完全相同<xref:System.String>列印系統物件，包括大小寫的屬性。

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Submitter%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo> object must be spelled "Submitter", not "submitter".
trans-unit.target: 例如，<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo.Submitter%2A>屬性<xref:System.Printing.PrintSystemJobInfo>物件必須拼字 「 傳送者 「 不 」 傳送者 」。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to use this constructor to install a second printer that differs in its properties from an existing printer only in location, port, and shared status.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範如何使用這個建構函式，若要安裝不同的第二個印表機屬性與現有印表機只位置、 連接埠，以及共用的狀態。

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to a <see cref="T:System.String" /> value.
trans-unit.target: 提供由 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> (或這類屬性的指標) 至 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 值的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> that is converted.
Provides implicit conversion to a <see cref="T:System.String" /> value from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" />.
trans-unit.target: 提供由指標的 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 值至 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: An implicit conversion to a String value from a pointer to a PrintStringProperty object.
trans-unit.target: 從 PrintStringProperty 物件指標到 String 值的隱含轉換。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> represents.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintStringProperty" /> 表示的屬性值。
